@node REQUEST "ABC-Patterns.guide/My Request"

   MY REQUEST:
   ~~~~~~~~~~~
   Because I believe it is ridiculous to require any amount of money for
   the right to use one or two patterns, I decided to release this package
   as @{" MAILWARE! " link COPYRIGHT}

   I would be happy to receive any @{"mail" link ADDRESS} considering ABC-PATTERNS because I
   want to know whether anyone likes them, or not.

   If you think they are ugly or useless, please tell me why you think so.

@endnode
